comment.body: 5 regular #transits, period 7.5 days; in all quarters.
Not sure here, but the object seems to be steadily growing in brighness over the recorder period, long period variable or nova??
I see transits from multiple planets #multiplanet #transit
Possible transit feature located at day 16.
Possible transit features located at days 6 and 20.
Possible transit feature located at day 21.

Star no. 2 could be a problem (i.e. it may be a BGEB).
